OL,8,GOne of our most requested ‘space’
OL,9,Gthemed films. Contact is adaptation of
OL,10,GCarl Sagan's book on how we may
OL,11,Gencounter alien life. A message is
OL,12,Greceived from deep space with
OL,13,Ginstructions for a new type of craft.
OL,14,GWhat follows is politics, lies and
OL,15,Gwonder. It eerily echos our current
OL,16,Gtimes. The cinematography alone makes
OL,17,Gthis worth a watch. How did they shoot
OL,18,Gthe scene with the bathroom cabinet?
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
